value.name: The Big Shot Game Show
value.overview: Brazilian entrepreneurs pitch their ideas to an audience and celebrity judges. But to win R$200,000, they’ll also have to navigate tough challenges.

value.name: Gigant Big-Shot Tsukasa
value.original_name: 超爆裂異次元メンコバトル ギガントシューター つかさ

value.name: Big Shot
value.overview: Naïve, young Tian Si Si, the apple of her father's eye and the sole heir to her family's riches, believes that she is in love with the great romantic hero, Qin Ge of the Meteor Clan. She dreams of traveling the martial arts world, actually meeting Qin Ge and having adventures just like many of the stories that she has read and heard. From childhood, she has been betrothed to the younger son of General Yang, Yang Fan, whom she despises.

value.name: The Big Shot with Bethenny
value.overview: The next generation of business moguls compete for a chance to be second-in-command to business tycoon and Skinnygirl founder Bethenny Frankel, and win a coveted position working on her executive team. Through a series of real-life tasks and challenges, each aspiring mogul will be tested to see how far they can push their creativity and determination to rise to the top.

value.name: Over Goddess
value.overview: The Dao Sovereign, a cold and peerless deity reigning supreme across all realms, takes in young girls destined to become future overlords of the cosmos as his disciples. Together, they embark on a perilous adventure to alter the fate of the multiverse—a fate hurtling toward annihilation. Faced with daunting trials and insurmountable challenges, can they overcome the odds, pass the ultimate tests, and forge a new world from the ashes of the old?
